24:50.256 --> 24:53.157
- [Abbie] You've
said this before.

24:54.125 --> 24:55.192
- I mean it.

24:58.196 --> 25:00.798
- Have you been going to AA?

25:03.802 --> 25:07.037
If you do want to
be part of her life,

25:07.906 --> 25:10.040
you have to start
making a contribution,

25:10.042 --> 25:12.543
really being there for her.

25:14.646 --> 25:17.081
And you need to start
putting down roots.

25:17.083 --> 25:19.283
When was the last
time I saw you?

25:19.285 --> 25:20.951
When? A year ago?

25:22.888 --> 25:23.787
And,

25:23.789 --> 25:28.659
I don't even know where
you're living anymore.

25:29.995 --> 25:31.862
Are you even listening to me?

25:31.864 --> 25:36.100
- Yeah, I'm listening, I just
have something in my eye.

25:37.636 --> 25:39.036
I think I got it.

25:39.038 --> 25:41.171
I'm listening. I'm sorry.

25:42.607 --> 25:46.644
- I need you to start
helping out with money.

25:46.646 --> 25:48.946
It's hard on Liz
and me financially.

25:48.948 --> 25:51.916
Peter's going away
to college soon.

25:53.919 --> 25:55.286
And it's not fair,

25:57.122 --> 25:58.222
to me or Alice.

26:14.339 --> 26:15.873
- [Sherry] Hey.

26:20.779 --> 26:21.979
- Hey. Here you go.

26:21.981 --> 26:24.048
- [Sherry] I'm starving.

26:24.983 --> 26:26.617
- You haven't changed.

26:26.619 --> 26:29.186
- No, I haven't been home yet.

26:31.923 --> 26:33.123
When do you get off?

26:33.125 --> 26:35.359
- In an hour, but it's
pretty dead today.

26:35.361 --> 26:36.860
- So stay a minute.

26:36.862 --> 26:39.296
- I can stay a little while.

26:39.298 --> 26:41.365
What do you think of the burger?

26:41.367 --> 26:44.001
- It's a little
dry, but it's fine.

26:44.003 --> 26:46.136
- Yeah, french fries
are soggy here, too.

26:46.138 --> 26:48.005
- Maybe you should
get a new cook.

26:48.007 --> 26:51.075
- A good cook is hard to find.

26:51.077 --> 26:53.711
Do you see that guy, over
there, walking to his car?

26:53.713 --> 26:55.646
Do you remember him?

26:55.648 --> 26:58.048
He was our 11th grade
chemistry teacher.

26:58.050 --> 26:59.050
- Mm.

26:59.985 --> 27:01.652
Mr. Williams.

27:01.654 --> 27:02.886
- I just find it so weird

27:02.888 --> 27:05.656
to see a teacher outside
the context of school.

27:05.658 --> 27:08.225
Like, they don't belong
in the real world.

27:08.227 --> 27:11.128
There's school and then
there's normal life.

27:11.130 --> 27:12.396
- Well, we're not
in school anymore.

27:12.398 --> 27:14.765
- I know, I just
find it kinda sad.

27:14.767 --> 27:18.736
They're normal people, just
like us, but no purpose.

27:18.738 --> 27:21.872
- I'm sure Mr.
Williams has a purpose.

27:21.874 --> 27:24.341
He probably has a
family of some sort.

27:24.343 --> 27:26.977
- Comes in here
quite often alone.

27:26.979 --> 27:30.214
But it didn't seem like a
wife or date or anything.

27:30.216 --> 27:32.082
More like a sister.

27:33.284 --> 27:36.053
- Well, maybe he has
a hobby or something,

27:36.055 --> 27:38.288
like fishing or sailing or

27:39.157 --> 27:41.091
something middle-aged people do.

27:41.093 --> 27:43.227
- I hope that
doesn't happen to us.

27:43.229 --> 27:44.061
- It won't.

27:44.063 --> 27:46.063
- Yeah? How do you know?

27:46.065 --> 27:47.898
- Well,

27:47.900 --> 27:50.200
I was thinking the other day,

27:51.670 --> 27:54.204
we could open up our own salon.

27:54.206 --> 27:56.073
Maybe make a little money.

27:56.075 --> 27:58.308
- What are you talking about?

27:58.310 --> 28:02.146
- I just thought we could do
something more substantial.

28:02.148 --> 28:05.983
You could do hair, manage
the place, potentially.

28:05.985 --> 28:07.985
- A beauty salon.
- Yeah.

28:07.987 --> 28:10.788
It would be a beauty salon.

28:10.790 --> 28:13.157
- You done with this?
- Mm-hmm.

28:15.126 --> 28:17.361
- I like the idea, but where
would we get the money?

28:17.363 --> 28:19.163
I don't have enough clients
to support a business yet,

28:19.165 --> 28:23.233
and you're not the
most reliable person.

28:23.235 --> 28:24.835
- That's not true.

28:24.837 --> 28:26.136
I'm getting better.

28:26.138 --> 28:29.206
I'm going to my meetings more.

28:29.208 --> 28:32.910
I'm trying to bring
Alice back into my life.

28:32.912 --> 28:35.145
We'll figure it
out as we go along.

28:35.147 --> 28:38.248
- This isn't just some
crazy fantasy of yours?

28:38.250 --> 28:41.118
- This is the real thing.

28:41.120 --> 28:44.054
I'm thinking more and more
about my future these days.

28:44.056 --> 28:45.089
- Yeah? How's that?

28:45.091 --> 28:46.824
- I'm thinking about

28:47.959 --> 28:50.227
my actions and opportunities.

28:50.229 --> 28:53.263
I'm laying the groundwork
to prepare myself

28:53.265 --> 28:54.865
for success and happiness...

28:54.867 --> 28:57.134
- That is nonsense.
- I'm serious.

28:57.136 --> 28:58.402
Very serious.
- All right.

28:58.404 --> 29:01.238
Well, I'll believe
it when I see it.

29:34.205 --> 29:36.807
- Um, nice seeing you again.

29:39.410 --> 29:41.945
Good, I've been going
here for four years now,

29:41.947 --> 29:43.447
and, um, it helps, you know.

29:43.449 --> 29:45.115
- Yeah.

29:45.117 --> 29:47.284
- [Man] So, you're really
welcome. Let me know.

29:47.286 --> 29:48.485
- Cool.

29:48.487 --> 29:50.420
- [Man] All right.
I'll see you in there?

29:50.422 --> 29:51.321
- Yeah.
- Okay.

29:51.323 --> 29:52.990
- Be right there.

29:54.225 --> 29:56.293
- Okay. Good seeing you.

29:57.295 --> 29:59.096
All right, see you soon.

29:59.098 --> 30:00.898
- See ya.
- All right.

30:22.954 --> 30:25.355
(wretching)

30:31.062 --> 30:32.930
- Want some help?

30:32.932 --> 30:34.531
- [Trish] No, I'll be fine.

30:34.533 --> 30:35.999
Just mind your own business.

30:36.001 --> 30:39.403
- I'm sorry, I'm just trying
to do a decent thing here

30:39.405 --> 30:40.470
and help you out.

30:40.472 --> 30:43.440
- Oh my god, just fuck off.

30:43.442 --> 30:46.543
(wretching)

30:46.545 --> 30:49.346
(toilet flushes)

30:53.418 --> 30:55.285
- [Bartender] Do
you want anything?

30:55.287 --> 30:59.156
- I'll have a whiskey
on the rocks, please.

31:16.407 --> 31:17.407
Are you alone?

31:24.115 --> 31:25.949
Are you a little shy?

31:30.955 --> 31:32.656
What are you drinking?

31:41.065 --> 31:44.201
You know, you didn't
have to do that.

32:04.188 --> 32:06.256
- [Man] Unlock the door?

32:13.498 --> 32:15.499
- Hey, what do you want from me?

32:15.501 --> 32:16.501
Get off me.

32:36.087 --> 32:39.056
- You shouldn't smoke in here.

32:39.058 --> 32:41.558
I don't want you
to get kicked out.

32:41.560 --> 32:44.227
- I can read. I see the sign.

32:52.570 --> 32:54.571
If you're so worried.

32:58.109 --> 33:00.477
Ow.
(laughing)

33:06.384 --> 33:09.987
Now we have nothing
to worry about, see?

33:14.058 --> 33:16.193
Can I ask you a question?

33:17.462 --> 33:21.264
Who were you waiting
for, at the bar earlier?

33:23.701 --> 33:24.701
- My wife.

33:27.739 --> 33:29.172
I'm separated.

33:31.476 --> 33:34.478
- How long have
you been separated?

33:35.313 --> 33:36.480
- Six months.

33:37.415 --> 33:40.650
I guess some things
aren't meant to be.

33:43.121 --> 33:45.055
- I saw a movie on TV recently.

33:45.057 --> 33:47.290
It's called Starting Over,

33:48.359 --> 33:51.061
with that girl
from Murphy Brown.

33:52.030 --> 33:53.663
- Candace Bergen?
- Yeah.

33:53.665 --> 33:55.766
Candace Bergen.

33:55.768 --> 33:57.501
She's not the lead
in it, though.

33:57.503 --> 34:00.570
It mainly centers
around Burt Reynolds.

34:00.572 --> 34:04.541
And he leaves his wife 'cause
she's been cheating on him,

34:04.543 --> 34:08.578
and he moves from New York to
Boston to start a new life.

34:09.580 --> 34:12.616
And he meets this girl there.

34:12.618 --> 34:14.551
She may not be as pretty
as Candace Bergen,

34:14.553 --> 34:15.652
but she's

34:17.487 --> 34:19.656
she's reliable and sweet.

34:20.690 --> 34:23.693
- Is there a lesson
in this for me?

34:24.762 --> 34:26.163
- I thought you'd
like to see the movie.

34:26.165 --> 34:29.433
You might find something
relatable in it.

34:29.435 --> 34:33.837
Like what life is like
for adults after marriage.

34:33.839 --> 34:35.806
It's pretty funny, too.

34:37.108 --> 34:38.641
I'm gonna go to bed.

35:04.135 --> 35:06.303
Am I gonna see you again?

35:07.472 --> 35:10.774
- I left my number on the table.

35:10.776 --> 35:12.309
Give me a call.

35:14.378 --> 35:15.378
- Goodbye.

35:16.581 --> 35:17.647
- Goodbye.

35:35.633 --> 35:36.900
- [Sherry Reading]
There must be something

35:36.902 --> 35:40.804
that you want in life
more than anything else.

35:42.507 --> 35:44.774
As a door-to-door
makeup saleswoman,

35:44.776 --> 35:48.545
I will not settle for
less than I deserve.

35:49.547 --> 35:52.649
I will continue to seek myself.

35:52.651 --> 35:54.651
My place is at the top.

36:09.267 --> 36:10.267
Hello?

36:16.474 --> 36:17.774
Is anyone in here?

36:36.527 --> 36:38.562
- Oh, hello.
- Hi.

36:38.564 --> 36:40.197
- [Woman] Were you
interested in the space?

36:40.199 --> 36:42.365
- I'm sorry, I didn't
mean to just barge in.

36:42.367 --> 36:43.767
- No, that's quite all right.

36:43.769 --> 36:45.735
You just missed the owner.

36:45.737 --> 36:47.204
I'm leaving in
just a few minutes,

36:47.206 --> 36:48.405
but if you have any questions,

36:48.407 --> 36:49.940
I'd be happy to
answer them for you.

36:49.942 --> 36:52.342
- That would be lovely.

36:52.344 --> 36:54.611
Well, obviously it needs a
little bit of paint, but...

36:54.613 --> 36:58.582
- Yeah, it needs some work,
but then, don't we all?

36:58.584 --> 37:01.251
I think it has great potential.

37:01.253 --> 37:02.953
- The carpet, also,
is a little much.

37:02.955 --> 37:05.522
But you can remove
that easily, right?

37:05.524 --> 37:07.824
- [Woman] Carpet is always
replaceable, absolutely.

37:07.826 --> 37:10.260
- I think it might be perfect
for what I'm looking for,

37:10.262 --> 37:12.362
- What kind of
business are you in,

37:12.364 --> 37:12.996
if you don't mind my asking?

37:12.998 --> 37:14.431
- It's a beauty salon.

37:14.433 --> 37:15.865
- Oh, well there you go.

37:15.867 --> 37:18.535
I think this would be
perfect for a salon.

37:18.537 --> 37:19.703
- I'm a makeup artist.

37:19.705 --> 37:21.938
- Are you, really?
Well, that's wonderful.

37:21.940 --> 37:23.873
Listen, if you're
serious about...

37:23.875 --> 37:25.775
- I am serious.

37:25.777 --> 37:28.278
- [Woman] Give me a call.

37:28.280 --> 37:30.413
- Susan, I will
call you tomorrow.

37:30.415 --> 37:31.748
- Very good, and
what's your name?

37:31.750 --> 37:34.484
- [Susan] Sherry Graham, very
nice to meet you, Sherry.

37:34.486 --> 37:37.454
- You too, Susan,
nice to meet you.

37:41.025 --> 37:42.559
- [Recording] You've
reached Abbie and Liz.

37:42.561 --> 37:44.761
Please leave a detailed
message after the beep.

37:44.763 --> 37:45.729
(beeping)

37:45.731 --> 37:50.533
So I thought a lot
about what you said,

37:50.535 --> 37:55.538
about money and contributing
financially to Alice's life.

37:55.540 --> 37:56.906
And I have a plan.

37:58.509 --> 38:00.510
I didn't have a
chance to tell you.

38:00.512 --> 38:03.413
I'm going to open
up my own salon.

38:04.482 --> 38:05.782
I have an appointment
already scheduled

38:05.784 --> 38:07.951
with a bank loan manager.

38:07.953 --> 38:09.286
So everything will be fine.

38:09.288 --> 38:10.620
I'll let you know how it goes.

38:10.622 --> 38:11.788
Wish me luck.

38:13.291 --> 38:14.758
Lay the groundwork.

38:18.529 --> 38:20.930
Prepare yourself for success

38:21.999 --> 38:23.433
and happiness.

38:27.438 --> 38:29.339
Success and happiness.

38:47.325 --> 38:49.759
- Hello, hi there, Alan Gilmore.

38:49.761 --> 38:51.561
- [Sherry] It's so nice
to meet you, Mr. Gilmore.

38:51.563 --> 38:52.729
- A pleasure to
meet you, as well.

38:52.731 --> 38:53.863
Please, take a seat.

38:53.865 --> 38:54.998
- Thank you for seeing me today.

38:55.000 --> 38:56.833
- Sure, absolutely.

38:56.835 --> 38:59.436
- You have a lovely office.

38:59.438 --> 39:01.971
(laughing)

39:01.973 --> 39:03.039
- Thank you.

39:04.342 --> 39:05.842
The branch I just
transferred in from

39:05.844 --> 39:09.346
was a nicer office, but
that's very kind of you.

39:09.348 --> 39:11.781
- And that, did you make that?

39:11.783 --> 39:13.817
- No, no, it was here.

39:13.819 --> 39:15.785
Everything was
here, when I came.

39:15.787 --> 39:18.888
Anyway, can I get you
a bottle of water?

39:18.890 --> 39:20.490
- If it's not too much trouble.

39:20.492 --> 39:21.424
- No, not at all.

39:21.426 --> 39:22.926
You want sparkling or still?

39:22.928 --> 39:23.928
- Still.

39:28.699 --> 39:29.833
- All right.
- Thank you.

39:29.835 --> 39:31.768
- There you are.

39:31.770 --> 39:35.372
So how can I, er, how
can I help you today?

39:35.374 --> 39:38.908
- I am inquiring
about a business loan.

39:38.910 --> 39:40.910
- Okay, what kind of business?

39:40.912 --> 39:43.613
- Well, my friend
and I, we have this

39:43.615 --> 39:46.916
idea to open up our own
salon, a beauty salon.

39:46.918 --> 39:50.854
- That sounds good. Do
you have a business plan?

39:50.856 --> 39:53.656
- I'm still working on that one.

39:53.658 --> 39:55.859
It's coming along, though.

39:55.861 --> 39:58.795
- [Alan] Okay, so today you
don't have the business plan.

39:58.797 --> 40:00.964
Did you bring a bank statement?

40:00.966 --> 40:02.432
Do you have any of the paperwork

40:02.434 --> 40:03.566
that you needed to fill out?

40:03.568 --> 40:04.834
- Mm-hmm.

40:04.836 --> 40:06.936
I have the forms here,

40:12.143 --> 40:13.977
filled out.

40:13.979 --> 40:15.111
- All right.

40:15.113 --> 40:17.480
This is a bank statement.

40:21.719 --> 40:22.986
Oh, it's just, it's just this?

40:22.988 --> 40:25.121
- Yeah, it's all there.

40:25.123 --> 40:26.123
- Oh.

40:29.627 --> 40:31.127
(sighs)

40:31.129 --> 40:34.931
- This is your overall
income from last year?

40:38.102 --> 40:39.469
- Yeah, well,

40:40.771 --> 40:41.771
it was, um,

40:42.973 --> 40:44.073
it was um,

40:45.910 --> 40:47.644
a tough year for me.

40:47.646 --> 40:48.778
- You can't,

40:48.780 --> 40:51.548
you can't smoke in here.

40:51.550 --> 40:53.016
- Oh, I'm sorry.

40:53.018 --> 40:54.851
- That's fine.

40:54.853 --> 40:57.987
- It's the rules.
- Yeah, I just didn't know.

40:57.989 --> 41:00.890
- That's okay.
- There was a rule.

41:03.994 --> 41:06.629
- Well, I, I'm not sure what's,

41:07.765 --> 41:10.834
how the bank can be
of service to you.

41:10.836 --> 41:13.102
- Well, you've
barely heard me out.

41:13.104 --> 41:14.871
It's a really good idea.

41:14.873 --> 41:16.039
- [Alan] Well, it might
be a very good idea,

41:16.041 --> 41:17.974
but you don't have
a business plan,

41:17.976 --> 41:22.712
and the numbers here
don't qualify for a loan.

41:22.714 --> 41:25.882
I'm not sure what
you were expecting.

41:25.884 --> 41:29.619
The bank has guidelines and
requirements for business loans.

41:29.621 --> 41:33.256
There's a pamphlet you
should take a look at.

41:34.792 --> 41:36.726
- I'm just getting started,

41:36.728 --> 41:37.728
and,

41:39.096 --> 41:41.598
you don't even know how
much I'm asking for.

41:41.600 --> 41:42.699
- Well, I'm sorry, ma'am...

41:42.701 --> 41:44.934
- I'm asking for $250,000.

41:46.136 --> 41:48.905
- Okay, if you're serious
about a loan of that size,

41:48.907 --> 41:50.974
you need to come prepared.

41:50.976 --> 41:52.909
- [Sherry] I'm serious.

41:52.911 --> 41:57.213
- Okay, so if you're serious
about a loan of that size,

41:57.215 --> 42:00.717
you need to provide the
bank with fiscal statements

42:00.719 --> 42:03.953
and other documentation
in order to get a loan.

42:03.955 --> 42:07.757
I'm, I'm sorry that you had
some sort of misunderstanding

42:07.759 --> 42:11.828
about this meeting, but,
it's not going to work.

42:13.998 --> 42:16.566
- [Sherry Reading] Don't get
lost in reckless emotions

42:16.568 --> 42:18.234
during moments of trial.

42:18.236 --> 42:22.772
Learn to lift yourself up
and harness positive energy.

42:22.774 --> 42:25.942
Go to work with a
smile on your face.

42:42.693 --> 42:44.227
- [Sherry] I was wondering
if I could introduce you

42:44.229 --> 42:45.862
to our beauty line.

42:45.864 --> 42:48.965
It would only take two
minutes of your time today.

42:48.967 --> 42:51.334
- Well, it's really
not a great time.

42:51.336 --> 42:54.003
I'm under construction. I'm...

42:54.005 --> 42:56.172
- [Sherry] You're
under construction?

42:56.174 --> 42:58.207
Renovations? Oh, wow.

42:59.910 --> 43:01.644
And we have a
beautiful line here

43:01.646 --> 43:03.980
that I would love
to introduce you to.

43:03.982 --> 43:06.683
And we have wonderful
specials this season, as well.

43:06.685 --> 43:08.851
If you have two minutes...

43:34.244 --> 43:35.244
Oh, fuck.

43:42.620 --> 43:44.687
(sighs)

43:53.163 --> 43:55.298
Because you can read about
these tips in magazines,

43:55.300 --> 43:58.201
but they're never right
for everyone, right?

43:58.203 --> 44:02.238
That's what's great about
having a consultant come to you.

44:04.975 --> 44:05.975
Perfect.

44:07.945 --> 44:09.145
Let me show you.

44:10.714 --> 44:12.682
So, I've only done
the right side,

44:12.684 --> 44:14.283
so you can see the difference.

44:14.285 --> 44:15.952
- [Woman] Mm-hmm.

44:17.054 --> 44:18.955
- So your skin is just
a little more matte.

44:18.957 --> 44:21.090
- Mm-hmm.
- Perfect.

44:21.092 --> 44:23.926
So should we start off
with that, those three?

44:23.928 --> 44:26.062
- Well, what, how
much does it cost?

44:26.064 --> 44:27.230
How much is each?

44:27.232 --> 44:29.365
- This foundation is $15.

44:30.434 --> 44:32.402
The nail polish is $12.

44:33.404 --> 44:35.271
And the lipstick is 20.

44:35.273 --> 44:36.273
- Oh.

44:37.274 --> 44:39.742
Maybe I'll just take
the catalog and...

44:39.744 --> 44:41.778
- Okay. All right.

44:41.780 --> 44:43.713
I still want to leave you
those samples, though.

44:43.715 --> 44:47.083
- Okay, well thank you.
- All right?

44:47.085 --> 44:48.751
How about the lipstick?

44:48.753 --> 44:50.820
If I, usually it's 15.

44:50.822 --> 44:54.824
I said 20 right now,
I'm sorry, it's 20.

44:54.826 --> 44:57.093
Since it's your
very first lipstick,

44:57.095 --> 44:59.829
I could let it go for $15.

44:59.831 --> 45:00.463
What do you think?

45:00.465 --> 45:02.165
- [Woman] Um...

45:02.167 --> 45:04.467
- It does look beautiful on you.

